name   : test
title  : Ruby Test
summary: Ruby Universal Test Harness
created: 2011-07-23

description:
  Ruby Test is a universal test runner for Ruby
  test frameworks. It can handle any compliant
  test system, even running tests from multiple
  frameworks in a single pass.

authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer <transfire@gmail.com>

requirements:
  - ansi
  - detroit (build)

